React Events 2


- You can update regular JS values through standard practices and event handlers but the page will not update unless you declare a state variable.
- All event listeners in react have a vanilla JS handler equivalent expect for these, which behave differently from there closest equivalent. 
- Remember event handler functions must either be inside the same component or imported into the current JS file. 

